{"abstract":[{"text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"code":"textJustify: auto","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor.","type":"text"}],"type":"